long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
The one extension that every Chrome user should have.

BUILT TO HARNESS INFORMATION
Business pays big money for your browsing history.
Why not tap into that value yourself and study what you consume on the internet. Now you can choose when and what you want to store locally while you surf the web.

BUILT FOR PRODUCTIVITY- The smarter way to browse.
On average US internet users visit 130 web documents per day. That equates to 910 websites per week and up to 4,000 per month. Now it's easier to organize and make that information useful.

KNOW YOURSELF- A better bookmark.
Organize and notate every website visited automatically and save them into WebDoc folders. Take control of your journey on the internet with shareable Web Document folders and more....

NEW WEB APPROACH- Share your Web Docs
Find interesting information on the web? Now you can package all those pages into one shareable WebDocs Pro native file. Make notes on each website and share with other WebDoc Pro users.
